Package org.blockchainnative.metadata

Class MethodInfo<TParameterInfo extends ParameterInfo>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.blockchainnative.metadata.MethodInfo<TParameterInfo>
  • Type Parameters:
    TParameterInfo - Concrete type of the ParameterInfo objects used by MethodInfo
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EthereumMethodInfo, FabricMethodInfo
    public class MethodInfo<TParameterInfo extends ParameterInfo>
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds additional information about a smart contract method.

    It is recommended to use ContractInfoBuilder and its subtypes to construct instances of this class.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    ContractInfoBuilder, ContractInfo, ContractWrapperGenerator
